fields.title: Cupcakes Galore: She Codes Party Begins
fields.content: Boom! Cupcakes galore as She Coders bask in their glory after completing their Django Python website project!

fields.title: 'Donut' Miss This News!
fields.content: Donuts are the best food ever. Yummy donuts come in so many flavours. Lots of different colours and tastes too! Donuts are the best. She Coders actually made loads with their new friends, and they LOVE them!! There's nothing like having your favourite delicious treat on hand to make you feel good about life. The most favorite recipe from the cohort was 'Banoffee Pie' Donut. It gives something nice but comforting without being heavy.

fields.title: She Codes Cohort Celebrates
fields.content: Woot! Woot! The Brisbane She Codes Plus Cohort can hardly believe their luck! They will celebrate this week by coding with the incredible Shauna as restrictions lift and they are able to shake hands of the coding goddess herself in person at the Hub. Celebrations will continue with a social catch up and lunch filled with coffee, coding chat and champagne cheers!
